'''尼古拉斯·"尼克"·肖雷'''（{{lang-en|'''Nicholas "Nicky" Shorey'''}}，{{bd|1981年|2月19日|catidx=Shorey, Nicky}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，擔任[[左後衛|左後衛]]。他是少數曾分別在四級[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]上陣過的球員之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.avfc.co.uk/page/PlayerProfiles/0,,10265~22487,00.html |title=Nicky Shorey Profile |publisher=[[阿士東維拉足球會|''avfc.co.uk'']] |date= |accessdate=2009-11-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091120233659/http://www.avfc.co.uk/page/PlayerProfiles/0,,10265~22487,00.html |archivedate=2009年11月20日 |df= }}</ref></small>。

==生平==
===球會===
;奧連特
梳利在足球事業始於1998年在[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|莱顿东方]]擔任學徒球員<ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-01-24 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6288625.stm |title=The secret of Shorey's success |publisher=[[BBC|BBC體育]] |accessdate=2007-01-25 |archive-date=2007-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070127154250/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6288625.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後升上一隊，在1999/2000年賽季和2000/01年賽季間中有機會代表奧連特在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|丙組〈第四級〉聯賽]]上陣，其間吸引了當時尚在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組〈第三級〉聯賽]]角逐的[[雷丁足球俱樂部|雷丁]]主教練[[阿兰·帕德鲁|-{zh-hans:帕德鲁; zh-hk:柏祖;}-]]（Alan Pardew）。

;雷丁
梳利在2001年2月10日轉會[[雷丁足球俱樂部|雷丁]]，轉會費25,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2001-02-10 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/1160054.stm |title=Reading complete Shorey deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC體育]] |accessdate=2007-01-25}}</ref>，梳利很快融入球隊，成為一隊的主力成員，雷丁取得聯賽亞軍並獲得升班[[英格蘭足球聯賽|甲組〈第二級〉聯賽]]的資格，其出色的表現導致球隊在季後放棄原本擔任左閘的[[馬特·羅賓遜|馬特·羅賓遜]]（Matt Robinson）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/1948125.stm |title=Reading release trio |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-24 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307201651/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/1948125.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2002年10月28日主場對[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|巴拉福特]]，梳利射入個人首個入球兼協助球隊1-0獲勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2356611.stm |title=Reading 1-0 Bradford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-10-28 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2003-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030817060713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2356611.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；2003年4月15日主場5-1大破[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]，梳利射入一個[[十二碼|十二碼]]，確保雷丁取得升班附加賽資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2935377.stm |title=Reading 5-1 Preston |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-04-15 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310074206/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2935377.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但在首輪兩回合累計1-3負於[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3013647.stm |title=Wolves edge past Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-05-10 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307033442/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3013647.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2003年8月9日聯賽揭幕戰作客[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，下半場因攔跌對方「單刀」球員而被罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3113045.stm |title=Ipswich 1-1 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-08-09 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715114425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3113045.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2003年3月因受[[細菌|細菌]]感染而缺席球季餘下比賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/3549069.stm |title=Illness strikes Royals |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-03-19 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2004-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040419234130/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/3549069.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2004/05年球季梳利為雷丁在更名為[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|冠軍聯賽]]中上陣44場及射入3球，卻在季末操練時弄傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]而缺席最後兩場比賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/4508833.stm |title=Shorey steps up comeback attempt |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-03 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306235317/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/4508833.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，雷丁因輸掉對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]及[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]這兩場而失去附加賽席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500843.stm |title=Wigan 3-1 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-08 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2012-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327083504/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500843.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他被[[BBC|BBC體育網站]]選為「英冠無名英雄」（The Unsung Hero）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/4540851.stm |title=The alternative awards: The players |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-18 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219175900/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/4540851.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006年4月23日梳利入選「2006年[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英冠|英冠]][[PFA年度最佳陣容#2006年|年度最佳陣容]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/4935884.stm |title=Gerrard named player of the year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-04-23 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908033508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4935884.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，[[2005年至2006年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|這球季]]雷丁以破紀錄的106分贏取[[英冠|英冠]]聯賽冠軍及升班[[英超|英超]]。8月1日，梳利與球隊簽下新合約直至2009年6月屆滿<ref name="contract August 2006">{{cite news |language=en |date=2006-08-01 |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~875443,00.html |title=Shorey extends his contract and commits to the Royals until summer of 2009 |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2006-10-16 }}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年賽季]]是梳利足球生涯中很重要的一季，梳利在首個頂級聯賽球季出色的表現令他首度獲[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]徵召。2006年11月12日主場對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，梳利上半場射入為球隊扳平1-1，是個人首個[[英超|英超]]入球，並扭轉形勢，反勝3-1完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6116256.stm |title=Reading 3-1 Tottenham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-12 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306005124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6116256.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。該季雷丁最終獲得[[英超|英超]]第8位，梳利在2007年5月5日被雷丁球迷選為該季的「賽季最佳球員」的第二名<ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-05-05 |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1021460,00.html |title=Ingimarsson is crowned Royals' player of the season after great campaign |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2007-05-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805163130/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1021460,00.html |archivedate=2012-08-05 }}</ref>。賽季尾很多球會欣賞梳利的表現，傳聞將他的名字與[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]及[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]扯上關係<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6243640.stm |title=Royals hold Shorey and Lita talks |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-06-26 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2007-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071207121348/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6243640.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，尚餘兩年合約的梳利拒絕續約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2640026,00.html |title=Shorey rejects Royals deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-08-04 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905230724/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2640026,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而韋斯咸正式出價500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]求購<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6968808.stm |title=West Ham make £5m bid for Shorey |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-29 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307193446/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6968808.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，被雷丁推卻<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2695506,00.html |title=Hammers fail in Shorey bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-08-30 |accessdate=2009-11-25}}</ref></small>，但梳利不排除在冬季轉會窗離隊的可能<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6982269.stm |title=Shorey cagey over Reading future |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-06 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2007-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071207010059/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6982269.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年12月17日雷丁與梳利仍為新約進行談判<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2972642,00.html |title=Shorey - Talks ongoing |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-12-17 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905163331/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2972642,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但梳利表示除非英超「''Big Four''」其一隊邀請，否則不會離隊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2976894,00.html |title=Shorey drops Royals hint |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-12-15 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080904221749/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2976894,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年2月14日梳利決定將續約問題留待季後才作決定<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3146055,00.html |title=Shorey stalls on new deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-02-14 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906122654/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3146055,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，在雙方為合約問題拖拖拉拉時，雷丁在聯賽已跌至降班邊緣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7226497.stm |title=Shorey blasts Reading performance |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-04 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209144735/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7226497.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終在[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|球季]]煞科日確定降班<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7381785.stm |title=Derby 0-4 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-11 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430023301/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7381785.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，據報導梳利與[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]和[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]商討轉會事宜<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11065_3735156,00.html |title=Harry admits Shorey liking |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-06-25 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905013055/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11065_3735156,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/gossip_and_transfers/7530205.stm |title=Tuesday's gossip column |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-29 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2008-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080802030840/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/gossip_and_transfers/7530205.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

;阿士東維拉
2008年8月8日，阿士東維拉完成了梳利的轉會，簽下3年合約，轉會費未有公布<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2008-08-07 |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1360664,00.html |title=Shorey signs for Villa |publisher=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2008-08-07 |archive-date=2008-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828184243/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1360664,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>，但他的母會[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|莱顿东方]]可獲得15%分紅<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/7523310.stm |title=Orient wait for Shorey sale bonus |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-24 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307024339/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/7523310.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。梳利表示很喜愛雷丁，或將來有機會重回[[雷丁足球俱樂部|雷丁]]踢球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2008-08-11 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7553547.stm |title=I would return to Royals - Shorey |publisher=[[BBC|BBC體育]] |accessdate=2008-08-11 |archive-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224212650/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/7553547.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。梳利加盟後穿上已離隊的[[加利·卡希爾|加利·卡希爾]]的21號球衣。他在[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]作客4-1擊敗[[Fimleikafélag_Hafnarfjarðar|夏拿佐杜亞]]（FH Hafnarfjordur）首度為維拉上陣。

2008年11月9日維拉主場對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]，賽前有機會晉身四強的維拉卻因守將的兩次錯失而落敗，上半場34分鐘[[斯图尔特·唐宁|唐寧]]長傳入禁區，梳利試圖用胸口解圍卻撞了給[[通恰伊·桑利|端基]]近門6碼射入，最終1-2完場痛失3分<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7709039.stm |title=Aston Villa 1-2 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-09 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090120133446/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7709039.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]於70分鐘將梳利換出，自此他便失去正選席位，[[卢克·扬|魯克·楊格]]調任左閘<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7853217.stm |title=Young happy to stay at left-back |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130092745/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7853217.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而其空缺則由[[卡洛斯·库拉尔|古拿]]、[[格力·加特拿|格力·加特拿]]、[[尼祖·李奧曲加|李奧曲加]]或[[詹姆斯·米尔纳|占士·米拿]]瓜代<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7960789.stm |title=Players must be flexible - Wright |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-24 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331180415/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7960789.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但連串的防守失誤，包括0-5大敗於[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]腳下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7937107.stm |title=Liverpool 5-0 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-22 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090322115022/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7937107.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，馬田·奧尼爾惟有在季末再派梳利上陣，將魯克·楊格調回慣常的右閘，於4月5日作客[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]復任正選<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7972801.stm |title=Man Utd 3-2 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-05 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091203070611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7972801.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

雖然領隊馬田·奧尼爾一再聲明梳利是包括在其未來大計中<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5201147,00.html |title=O'Neill - Shorey is staying |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-04-17 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015225201/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5201147,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但在2009年傳媒廣泛報導這名前雷丁守將未能確定其是否繼續留效維拉<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12876_5218732,00.html |title=Shorey unsure of future |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-04-21 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015225109/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12876_5218732,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5356048,00.html |title=Shorey still unsure of future |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-05-30 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601094838/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5356048,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5498022,00.html |title=Shorey future remains unclear |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015225141/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5498022,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，然而梳利在[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]在維拉開季頭4場的比賽擔任正選<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8197493.stm |title=Aston Villa 0-2 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-15 |accessdate=2009-12-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8209432.stm |title=Rapid Vienna 1-0 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2009-12-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8209624.stm |title=Liverpool 1-3 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-24 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091002072729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8209624.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2009年9月1日有傳聞梳利會被外借到[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]一整個球季，在造訪[[法頓公園球場|法頓公園球場]]後，雙方未能就合作達成協議，梳利仍然留在維拉。

[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]季初[[史提芬·禾洛克|禾洛克]]自[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]來投後<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/2613923/Aston-Villas-Nicky-Shorey-is-ready-to-battle-Stephen-Warnock-for-a-place-in-the-team.html |title=Villa's Nicky is ready for Wor |publisher=[[太陽報|''thesun.co.uk'']] |date=2009-08-29 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090901131444/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/2613923/Aston-Villas-Nicky-Shorey-is-ready-to-battle-Stephen-Warnock-for-a-place-in-the-team.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，梳利再次被打入冷宮。2009年11月24日，本季僅6次代表維拉上陣的梳利被外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]直到12月尾<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8376008.stm |title=Forest bring in full-back Shorey |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-24 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2009-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091127084323/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8376008.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。11月28日首次上陣主場迎戰[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]，協助球隊大勝4-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8375190.stm |title=Nottm Forest 4-1 Doncaster |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-28 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091130060530/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8375190.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。外借期間為森林上陣7場，於後5場比賽協助球隊保持清白之軀，獲森林延長借用到1月尾<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8436295.stm |title=Nottingham Forest extend Nicky Shorey loan from Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-31 |accessdate=2010-01-01 |archive-date=2010-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122053301/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8436295.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年1月27日由於禾洛克脛骨受傷，馬田·奧尼爾召回梳利，期間合共為森林上陣9場，更協助球隊高據聯賽榜次席，但回歸首仗對[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，馬田·奧尼爾仍然將魯克·楊格調任左閘，梳利繼續坐冷板凳<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8484143.stm |title=Aston Villa recall Shorey from Nottingham Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-27 |accessdate=2010-01-28 |archive-date=2010-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131011336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8484143.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。於2月1日再被外借到[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]直到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5909558,00.html |title=Fulham seal Shorey loan |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-01 |accessdate=2010-02-02 |archive-date=2010-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203010136/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5909558,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

;西布朗
2010年8月9日梳利轉投鄰近剛升班返回[[英超|英超]]的[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]，簽約兩年加一年優先續約，轉會費沒有透露<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/8896870.stm |title=West Brom boss Di Matteo signs Nicky Shorey |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-09 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |archive-date=2010-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100809191701/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/8896870.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
由於在[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]梳利在[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]有出色的表現，雷丁球迷特別為他編了一首名為《梳利入選英格蘭》（''Shorey For England''）的打氣歌<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-01-14 |url=http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article2152521.ece |title=Graduation earns a fanfare for Shorey |work=[[The_Independent|''independent.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2009-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071210054740/http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article2152521.ece |archivedate=2007-12-10 }}</ref></small>，在球季進行中，傳媒開始對當時尚未代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]的球員多加注意<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2006-11-13 |url=http://football.guardian.co.uk/Match_Report/0,,-69542,00.html |title=Shorey riposte kick-starts Royals' ascent |work=[[The_Guardian|''guardian.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070218111426/http://football.guardian.co.uk/Match_Report/0,,-69542,00.html |archive-date=2007-02-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-02-08 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6341653.stm |title=McClaren's learning curve |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2007-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070226040710/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6341653.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年5月25日梳利獲徵召加入[[英格蘭足球代表乙隊|英格蘭B隊]]在[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]主場[[摩亞球場|摩亞球場]]（Turf Moor）對陣[[阿爾巴尼亞國家足球隊|阿爾巴尼亞]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-05-10 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6644157.stm |title=Owen included in England B squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2007-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070910213626/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6644157.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，並獲派正選上陣，直到下半場73分鐘才被[[乔莱昂·莱斯科特|列史葛]]入替，當時英格蘭已領先3-1，紀錄一直維持到完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-05-25 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6670865.stm |title=England B 3-1 Albania |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6APKZG1kV?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6670865.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。球評家認為梳利的表現足以提升上國家隊<small><ref>{{cite news | language=en | date=2007-05-15 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6653937.stm | title=Garth Crooks' team of the season | publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | accessdate=2009-12-01 | archive-date=2009-01-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129124907/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6653937.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而於5月26日隨即獲得[[史提夫·麥卡倫|麥卡倫]]挑選加入[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]大軍名單中，備戰對[[巴西國家足球隊|巴西]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]及[[愛沙尼亞國家足球隊|愛沙尼亞]]的[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛|2008年歐國盃外圍賽]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-05-26 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6694743.stm |title=Beckham recalled to England squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2007-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071005195058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6694743.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2007年6月1日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]出戰巴西為梳利首次代表國家隊上陣，戰果1-1和氣終場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-06-01 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6696153.stm |title=England 1-1 Brazil |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216035439/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6696153.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其表現獲得讚賞<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-06-02 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/berkshire/content/articles/2007/06/02/shorey_clockwatch_070602_feature.shtml |title=Joel Hufford's Nicky Shorey clockwatch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Radio Berkshire |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2010-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100117051121/http://www.bbc.co.uk/berkshire/content/articles/2007/06/02/shorey_clockwatch_070602_feature.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-06-02 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?xml=/sport/2007/06/02/sfgeng02.xml |title=McClaren denied a famous victory |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|''telegraph.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2007-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070917065423/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?xml=%2Fsport%2F2007%2F06%2F02%2Fsfgeng02.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但對愛沙尼亞卻未能佔一席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-06-06 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6716859.stm |title=Estonia 0-3 England |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2009-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090523161823/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6716859.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在他獲得首頂國際賽喼帽一天後，他在[[雷丁|雷丁]]市郊辛菲特（Shinfield）舉行婚禮。

2007年8月22日梳利第二次代表國家隊上陣，同樣在溫布萊主場迎戰[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]，以1-2敗北<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-08-22 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6954720.stm |title=England 1-2 Germany |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2017-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815145047/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6954720.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

